#text: Welcome Friends! Thank you so much for visiting our team.
We're affectionately named after and connected to a kindred magical place full of renewal, re-birth and always future-facing. It's the volcanic phoenix powerhouse mountain
in Iceland (aka
and adopted by our teammates). Our team is committed to contribute to make a difference to deliver solutions that benefit humanity.

We're celebrating our multi-year organizational success of iterative agile product deliveries for our own products and valued clients. A clear testament to our team culture and how we work to progress on every front. Virtual, multinational and fully liability-insured team of specialists.
Nimble. Diverse. Experienced.
Voice-Driven. Data-Powered. AI-Wired. Practical solutions from ideas to best cost-effective production.
Our goal is to continuously develop mainstream concepts, designs (PoCs) and take them to great MVPs, builds and final RCs.
Applied science and useful knowledge application to build for humanity.
Iterating. Innovating. Improving.
* Full end-to-end technical product ownership (TPO)
* Replicable Data Science & AI apps and APIs
* We are hands-on & a highly-focused group of developers
* Our MVP delivery record is 98%+
* Met all agile project increment and release milestones 100% of the time
* We measure ourselves with meaningful benchmarks
* Reduced overall project CICD tooling costs by 80%
Calculate your TCO and cost savings
(utility apps to help reduce public stress)
for our apps, AI & integrations with relevant third-party APIs
Strengthening all of this is our silk-smooth CICD (aka DevOps). In practice by our team from concept to deployment and to final production CDN deployments with enterprise-grade security-hardening.

We are constantly iterating, innovating and improving our concepts, designs, builds, user-testing with core testing from the get-go and we're always trying our best to deploy feature-rich and uncomplicated products. We have implemented a culture to protect privacy, be compliant for HIPAA, GDPR, CCPA and have a solid SLA with independent replicable auditing.
Plus we offer real continuous human support and maintenance across the board.

We are a team of senior data scientists, full-stack developers and technical product owners. We're North America based, mostly-virtual and connect with all corners of the globe (offshore model). We have a successful rapport with many clients, vendors, partners and other specialist teammates around the world.
We are forward-looking thinkers.
Our outlook is global and cross many cultures, languages, locales, spanning our entire planet.
Integrating & Improving Integrations
- Imaging Informatics
- NLP Fulfillments and NLU
- Bias Reduction in AI
- NGS Phenotype Diagnoses
- Clinical Trials Analytics
